title: UFYB 175: QA: Business Building Thoughts & Getting Negative Feedback at Work
itunes:title: QA: Business Building Thoughts & Getting Negative Feedback at Work
description:
Do you feel pressured to have a “life goal” or to discover your “calling” in life? Do you struggle with defensiveness when receiving negative feedback at work? In today’s Listener Q&A episode, I’ll answer some common questions about work and entrepreneurship, and share the thoughts I used to scale my business from $50k to 1 million, and beyond.

Get full show notes and more information here: https://unfuckyourbrain.com/175
